[How very sad that these animals had to die from a horrible disease, a disease preventable by vaccination.

West Nile virus, EEE, and Western equine encephalitis come in a combination vaccine. Protecting your horse is easy. Vaccinate the animal.

Spray the horses with equine fly and mosquito repellant, and clean up breading grounds for mosquitoes. And be diligent to vaccinate your horse. - Mod.TG]
